# Magnifica response-page · password-gate configuration
#
# Required env-vars for alpha/magnifica-site. Add to the deployed .env
# (or .env.production) and to your local .env when working in this branch.
#
# Per HM-2026-06-02 PM: gesture-mode · long-lived cookie · shared-password
# between Hans and Olah (sent in the personal email · the URL + password
# travel together).
#
# See crearis:projects/magnifica/docs/howto-password-entry.md §4-§5 +
# server/middleware/00-magnifica-auth.ts.

# Shared password · sent in the personal email to Olah.
# HM-owned · do NOT commit a real value · the example here is a placeholder.
MAGNIFICA_PASSWORD=please-set-me-before-deploy

# Cookie lifetime in seconds · default 31536000 (1 year) per gesture-mode.
# Lower this if you want a stricter rotation; raise for very-long-living gesture.
# MAGNIFICA_COOKIE_MAX_AGE=31536000
